description:
## Why are we doing this work

We want to allow users to enable container scanning in the UI via an MR.

## Relevant links

* https://gitlab.com/groups/gitlab-org/-/epics/6334
* https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/issues/349902 introduces the GraphQL mutation for configuring Container Scanning.

